{"tid":413416,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日網票選「突然結婚會讓你大受打擊的女星」500名男性聯合要求女神永遠守身","createTime":"2017-09-25T12:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T12:25:12.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c8a00c462ed7bb7263690a64e24fddfea80f66","tid":413416,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T12:05:58.000Z","msg":"日本當紅女星武井咲年僅23歲就帶球閃婚，再度丟給演藝圈震撼彈，再加上佐佐木希宣布嫁給諧星渡部健，讓粉絲從年初一路心碎到現在。有網站以「突然結婚會讓你大受打擊的女星」為題，針對500名男性做問券調查，果然「我老婆」橋本千雪秒登冠軍，大家甚至嚴格要求女神「永遠守身！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/16730675_713344005513063_8403369035549077737_n.jpg?oh=dfbc84b4186cb385f378a7d5d5b58801&amp;oe=5A3D83E0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F16730675_713344005513063_8403369035549077737_n.jpg%3Foh%3Ddfbc84b4186cb385f378a7d5d5b58801%26oe%3D5A3D83E0&h=e6213cdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲男粉絲不敢想像千雪閃婚，要求「永遠純潔！」<br />\n<br />\n據《美麗Biranger》調查結果，橋本千雪榮登「結婚會大受打擊」女星冠軍，這效應全是來自《踩過界》激出的高人氣，儘管曾傳過幾次熱戀緋聞都不了了之。女星閃婚消息雖然時有所聞，她要是閃婚更是台日網友最不想聽到的消息，有人要求「我希望她永遠純潔無瑕」、「像傑尼斯一樣禁婚」、「真要結婚的話，嫁給Signal Wong（EU超時任務男主角）好了。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2819%2Fd2819728.jpg&h=51819e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲石原聰美穿搭引領潮流，男粉絲大喊「最不想看妳穿婚紗！」<br />\n<br />\n第二名則是才傳出婚訊石原聰美，因《朝5晚9》、《校閱女王》成為時尚教主，被男粉絲要求，「妳什麼都能穿！就是不能穿婚紗！」現年30歲的她和山下智久多次爆出熱戀緋聞，閃婚傳言更是登上熱搜關鍵字，本尊還沒說話大批網友已經先喊「LOST」，男粉坦言「我不想看她穿婚紗」、「是我療癒的來源，要是結婚我會憂鬱」，由於她曾說過「我30歲了，想珍惜重要的人」，疑似為結婚做準備的宣言，讓網友至今還在心驚膽跳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2819%2Fd2819729.jpg&h=9d2b9edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲深田恭子爆閃婚讓粉絲好害怕，「我的青春就結束了。」<br />\n<br />\n第三名則是34歲的深田恭子，從16歲因《神啊！請給我多一點時間》電翻男女粉絲，至今仍穩坐女神寶座，童顏加上魔鬼身材，透過社群網站公開辣照，IG追蹤人數突破160萬人。不過她也和龜梨和也爆出戀愛閃婚的傳言，最近還曬出抱姪子的照片噴發母愛，想婚氣氛越來越濃厚，男粉絲仍不甘心放手，「小深不要結婚啊」、「看起來很享受戀愛，希望她不要收手」、「她是我學生時代的女神，要是結婚了，我的青春也結束了！」<br />\n<br />\n以下10女星被男粉絲選為「聽到結婚心情會大受打擊」<br />\n<br />\n1.橋本千雪<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/elle_star/tracy-chu-dec-2016-wedding-cover/22/21555424-1-chi-HK/2_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Felle_star%2Ftracy-chu-dec-2016-wedding-cover%2F22%2F21555424-1-chi-HK%2F2_img_885_590.jpg&h=aa936e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.石原聰美<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2819%2Fd2819847.jpg&h=0ab0aeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.深田恭子<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819862.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2819%2Fd2819862.jpg&h=6ca68808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.有村架純<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2819%2Fd2819848.jpg&h=d390bc46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.長澤雅美<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819796.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2819%2Fd2819796.jpg&h=c65e12ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.桐谷美玲<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2819%2Fd2819723.jpg&h=0ceb8217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.吉岡里帆<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819793.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2819%2Fd2819793.jpg&h=8ebe1cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.綾瀨遙<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2819/d2819725.jpg\" data-thumbnail